{"tid":27053,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"跟隨 Apple！Galaxy S8 放棄 3.5mm 耳機插！","createTime":"2016-12-07T06:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T11:47:44.000Z","uid":7033,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7df92e42facb9bc18a5e6ec459b61dc76d5b1fc","tid":27053,"uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:00:05.000Z","msg":"iPhone 7 放棄 3.5mm 耳機插，到今日依然極具爭議。究竟其他手機品牌會跟隨還是反而將 3.5mm 插位變成賣點？現在看來很可能會集體淘汰 3.5mm 耳機插了。<br />\n<br />\n根據向來頗為可靠的消息來源，Samsung 決定跟隨 Apple 放棄 3.5mm 耳機插。第一部沒有耳機插的就是明年的旗艦機 Galaxy S8。正如 Apple 以 Lightning 插取代，Samsung 就會用 USB-C 作為新耳機插。換句話說，除非你買個新的 USB-C 耳機，否則就要用轉駁器才能在 Galaxy S8 使用現存耳機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.price.com.hk/news.php?sec_id=12&amp;id=7044\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.price.com.hk%2Fnews.php%3Fsec_id%3D12%26id%3D7044&d=X9zawEwOPtUB9tmiUFRPPWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=526976c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.price.com.hk/news.php?sec_id=12&amp;id=7044</a><br />\n<br />\n之前啲an狗唔係係咁笑apple on9既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9516682e1111cd914a47479c0b8a284a883ebc48","tid":27053,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:05:04.000Z","msg":"食花生"},{"pid":"ea55f8581f25f64a2b617689e1b63125f2b4f0bf","tid":27053,"uid":5734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:08:24.000Z","msg":"含到雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e82d3025df451744c7bef326b0654d3fa36ffa","tid":27053,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:10:23.000Z","msg":"死得仲快"},{"pid":"3e257c583d393e139ef1d0327431330e321af5d7","tid":27053,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:11:30.000Z","msg":"on9 samsung<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利伸an狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/b